      "2020": "The Contractor engaged CGG in 2016 to acquire 3D seismic data. The seismic vessel was intercepted by Togolese navy and frustrated the acquisition work. The matter still remains unresolved between Ghana and Togo.\nThe Contractor engaged CGG in 2016 to acquire 3D seismic data. The seismic vessel was intercepted by Togolese navy and frustrated the acquisition work. The matter still remains unresolved between Ghana and Togo.",
